aboutMe.title: About me
aboutMe.text: I’m a Software Engineer with a “can-do” vibe, a natural problem-solver, and a love for writing clean, efficient code. I’ve worked on a bunch of different projects, which has given me a solid sense of how to create real business impact. Always pushing myself to learn more and improve, I’m all about making an impact wherever I can.
